    "comment": "Rationale: Figure 1: immunogold labeling of TRPC1 and electron microscopy of the cerebellum showed postsynaptic and, to a lesser extend, presynaptic localization. Partial co-localization was observed for immunogold labelling for TRPC1 (5 nm) and mGluR1α /GRM1 (10 nm).\n\nBased on the known transmembrane topology of this protein, \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was selected.. Experimental description: Result sections: \"To assess the ultrastructural localization of TRPC1 we performed post-embedding immuno-electron microscopy on adult rat cerebellum (Fig. 1d).\"\n\nTRPC1 antibody (Alomone)",
